skins.shipDescription: Kizuna AI here, wearing a dress, coming at you! Be it concert or combat, I'll give it my all!
skins.selfIntroduction: This is the costume I wear for my concerts! I hope one day this port will be able to host a concert, too!
skins.acquisition: Kizuna AI here, wearing a dress, coming at you! Be it concert or combat, I'll give it my all!
skins.login: Welcome back! I got some singing lessons from Saratoga in preparation for my next concert. Give me your ear for a sec!
skins.details: What type of music do you listen to, Commander? I have a great artist recommendation for you! Her name's Kizuna AI... Oh wait, that's me!
skins.secretaryIdle1: That was great, Z35! Oh, hi, Commander! I just got to hear Z35 practice her singing!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Check it out, this thing is so flappy! You want me to jump? Too bad for you this isn't a skirt.
skins.secretaryIdle3: Huh? You think I'm cute? Uh-huh! I already knew that, but thanks!
skins.secretaryTouch: Oh, are you requesting a song? Sure thing, what do you wanna hear? I'll sing it for you!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: You want a high five? Let's do it! Yeeeaahhh!
